^I^I^I&nbsp;









LODSW


No operands


Load word at DS:[SI] into AX. Update SI.Algorithm:



AX = DS:[SI]
if DF = 0 then
^I
^ISI = SI + 2
^I
^Ielse
^I
^ISI = SI - 2
^I



Example:


ORG 100h

LEA SI, a1
MOV CX, 5

REP LODSW   ; finally there will be 555h in AX.

RET

a1 dw 111h, 222h, 333h, 444h, 555h



